Package letter

Class Summary
Constant A specialized subclass of Letter, which is used to represent an atomic generator of a free group.
LatexAdapter Converts instances of Letter to latex formatted text.
Letter An abstract class which is used to represent constants and variables.
LetterComparator Allows for uniform comparisons between Letter objects.
LetterFactory Singleton class which makes Constant and Variable objects.
Main A sample program based on the letter package.
Safety Specifies runtime safety settings for this package.
Variable A specialized subclass of Letter, which is used to represent an variables whose values can be elements of a free group.
